snippet.title: "Revue Starlight Re LIVE" Preview
snippet.description:
The Adventure Begins on Stage!
Preview video for Revue Starlight Re LIVE available now!

The theme song is "Discovery!", sung by the Starlight Kukugumi.

Don't miss it!

Pre-register for Revue Starlight Re LIVE now!

◆Official Website
https://www.en.revuestarlight-relive.com
